3. N-COUNT A bird's breast is the front part of its body. (鸟的) 胸脯 

例： The cock's breast is tinged with chestnut. 这只公鸡的胸脯带点栗色。 

4. N-SING The breast of a shirt, jacket, or coat is the part which covers the top part of the chest. (衬衫、外套、大衣等的) 胸部 

5. N-VAR You can refer to a piece of meat that is cut from the front of a bird or lamb as breast . (禽类或羔羊的) 胸脯肉 

